      "raw_text": "After a conference in Seattle\nlasting over two hours yesterday\nafternoon between the representa-\ntievs Of the Milwaukee, Great Nor.\nthern and Northern Pacific rail\nways and the corporations commit.\ntee of the city council, the commit\ntee recommended the granting OF\nthe Milwaukee franchise to enter\nthe city and reach the lands pur\nchased for dockage facilities on\nthe East waterway over Whatcom\navenue, and to connect with trans.\nfer tracks on Railroad avenue at\nYesler way under conditions which\nwere accepted by the Milwaukee\npeople without protest."
